description:
Watch Maralee Dawn & Friends Season 4 Episode 3 Coach Blows the Whistle on Vision Video

We love deer skin drums and dancing with the chief at Head-Smashed-in Buffalo Jump World  Heritage site! Butch’s coach brings an attitude adjustment, and they focus on team building skills. 

Maralee Dawn & Friends takes a refreshing and imaginative approach to Bible based children’s programming.  Each episode is jam-packed with original songs.  The action is fast paced as Master Ventriloquist Maralee Dawn and her unique puppet characters engage young viewers with adventures to exotic places, encounters with unusual creatures, and creative interactive projects.  Children assimilate the values and character qualities as naturally as eating ice cream!

Producer/Host: Maralee Dawn
Director: Christopher Bessette
Editor: OMNI Productions
Puppet Characters: Butch, Suzi, Andrew the Robot, D-Duck, D-Dog, Ms. Cratchet (Schoolteacher), Grandpa (Storyteller), Tommy (International Boy), Stephen (Southern Boy), Ms. Martin (Secretary Bird)

chapters.title: The people were to march, not fight
A victory by God's great might
Caring not what the people said
With courage marching day by day
March, march, march around the walls
March around the walls of Jericho
Seven times on the seventh day
